  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Ana and team up with companions to plant crops, click to collect resources, place various items, and enjoy a relaxing adventure in a magical and mysterious dream world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another peaceful night, the moon hung high, and its gentle light watched over everyone as they drifted off to sleep. To the melody of a music box, Ana had a dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In that place, the sky stretched both above and below. Broken stones and ruins drifted in a kaleidoscope of light, lost in the glow, while the floating clouds beneath them extended like land, carrying endless wonders. To find her scattered companions in the dream, Ana and Ura planted seeds, drawing strength from the crops to venture deeper into the heart of the dream...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distinctive characters and their little stories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/7a333db20e89d00a822c7cca06d8ae3c.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/7a333db20e89d00a822c7cca06d8ae3c.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple planting and idle gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant seeds, wait for crops to grow, and click to gather spiritual power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/2c45f2c1020b2f45148e94fe82a3211d.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/2c45f2c1020b2f45148e94fe82a3211d.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and place various items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and arrange unique items to automate harvesting and resource collection, speeding up spiritual power generation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/a1504630a3f18704f1197d04eedf31c8.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/a1504630a3f18704f1197d04eedf31c8.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your exploration and gradually unlock adorable interactions between characters in the story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.mp4?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Ana and team up with companions to plant crops, click to collect resources, place various items, and enjoy a relaxing adventure in a magical and mysterious dream world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another peaceful night, the moon hung high, and its gentle light watched over everyone as they drifted off to sleep. To the melody of a music box, Ana had a dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In that place, the sky stretched both above and below. Broken stones and ruins drifted in a kaleidoscope of light, lost in the glow, while the floating clouds beneath them extended like land, carrying endless wonders. To find her scattered companions in the dream, Ana and Ura planted seeds, drawing strength from the crops to venture deeper into the heart of the dream...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distinctive characters and their little stories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/7a333db20e89d00a822c7cca06d8ae3c.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/7a333db20e89d00a822c7cca06d8ae3c.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple planting and idle gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant seeds, wait for crops to grow, and click to gather spiritual power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/2c45f2c1020b2f45148e94fe82a3211d.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/2c45f2c1020b2f45148e94fe82a3211d.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and place various items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and arrange unique items to automate harvesting and resource collection, speeding up spiritual power generation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/a1504630a3f18704f1197d04eedf31c8.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/a1504630a3f18704f1197d04eedf31c8.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your exploration and gradually unlock adorable interactions between characters in the story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.poster.avif?t=1740802160\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.webm?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202490/extras/eafa64eff2b2760ca52431767949875f.mp4?t=1740802160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
